{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2018}} {{Infobox Officeholder | honorific-prefix = | name = F. X. Hadi Rudyatmo | honorific-suffix = | image = FX Hadi Rudyatmo.jpg | caption = | office = 16th Mayor of [[Surakarta]] | term_start = 19 October 2012<ref>[http://news.liputan6.com/read/444413/jumat-depan-gubernur-jateng-lantik-pengganti-jokowi Liputan 6.com]</ref> | term_end = | deputy = [[Achmad Purnomo]] | predecessor = [[Joko Widodo]] | successor = | office1 = Lieutenant Mayor of Surakarta | term_start1 = 28 July 2005 | term_end1 = 4 October 2012<ref>[http://news.detik.com/read/2012/10/15/133430/2062802/10/ini-kondisi-politik-di-solo-ketika-jokowi-dilantik-jadi-gubernur-dki?9922022 Detik.com]</ref> | mayor1 = [[Joko Widodo]] | predecessor1 = J. Suprapto | successor1 = [[Achmad Purnomo]] | office2 = Member of Surakarta City Council | term_start2 = 2004 | term_end2 = 2005 | birth_name = Fransiskus Xaverius Hadi Rudyatmo | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1960|02|13}} | birth_place = [[Surakarta]], [[Central Java]], [[Indonesia]] | death_date = | death_place = | restingplace = | restingplacecoordinates = | birthname = | nationality = [[Indonesia]] | party = [[Partai Demokrasi Indonesia Perjuangan|PDI Perjuangan]] | otherparty = <!--For additional political affiliations --> | spouse = Ny. Endang Prasetyaningsih Rudyatmo | partner = <!--For those with a domestic partner and not married --> | relations = | children = 5 | parents = | residence = | alma_mater = | occupation = | profession = | religion = [[Roman Catholic]] | signature = | website = | facebook = | facebookpage = | twitter = }}
'''Fransiskus Xaverius Hadi Rudyatmo''' (born 13 February 1960) is an [[Indonesia]]n politician and the current [[Mayor]] of [[Surakarta]]. His party is [[Indonesian Democratic Party – Struggle]] (PDI-P).
Before he was mayor, he had been elected into Surakarta's city council in 2004, and became the deputy mayor in 2005. After being reelected in 2010, he became the mayor when [[Joko Widodo]] became the [[Governor of Jakarta]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Profil F.X Hadi Rudyatmo |url=https://www.viva.co.id/siapa/read/160-fransiskus-xaverius-hadi-rudyatmo |accessdate=5 October 2018 |work=VIVA |language=id}}</ref> == References == {{reflist}}
